item.title: CVE-2020-5626|2024-08-04T08:39:25.686Z -- infoscience%20corporation -- logstorage%20and%20elc%20analytics
item.description: Logstorage version 8.0.0 and earlier, and ELC Analytics version 3.0.0 and earlier allow remote attackers to execute arbitrary OS commands via a specially crafted log file.
